  This app calculates upcoming dates for Scottish Civil Court Actions based on the court and type of court action. These results are provided as-is without any warranty or liability whatsoever. The information available on this website  <strong>should not</strong> be relied upon as a sole basis for responding/planning court action in Scotland. The data and calculations made by this site are indicative and strictly for information only. <strong>Court dates are subject to change and you should always check and confirm timings with the relevant Scottish court</strong>  If you have been served with, or intend to serve court action on an individual/ company and you are based in Scotland, you should <strong>seek professional legal advice in any event</strong>. Nothing on this website should be taken as legal advice.
